# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ All variables below are OPTIONAL.                              │
# │                                                                │
# │ Credentials can be configured via the monitor UI at            │
# │ http://localhost:3400 (Settings page / onboarding flow).       │
# │                                                                │
# │ If this .env file exists AND the settings DB is empty,         │
# │ these values are auto-imported on first boot as a convenience. │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

# Claude Code OAuth token (run `claude setup-token` to get one)
# CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=sk-ant-oat01-...

# GitHub PAT with repo scope (used by gh CLI, never exposed to LLM)
# GIT_TOKEN=ghp_...

# GitHub repo slug (owner/repo) - agent is GATED to only this repo
# GITHUB_REPO=your-org/SignalPilot

# Max budget per run in USD (default: 50)
# MAX_BUDGET_USD=50

# Benchmark data directory on host (default: D:\signalpilot-bench)
# SP_BENCHMARK_DIR=D:\signalpilot-bench
